"Well, the Lord be thanked, Princess," said Mary Bogdnovna, not hastening her steps. "You young ladies should not know anything about it." 
"But how is it the doctor from Moscow is not here yet?" said the princess. (In accord- ance with Lise's and Prince Andrew's wishes they had sent in good time to Moscow for a doctor and were expecting him at any mo- ment.)
